 MF = 2 Resonance Parameters                                      5837 1451
  A set of Reich-Moore resonance parameters (LRF=3, LCOMP=1) was  5837 1451
  evaluated by fitting transmission and capture yield data        5837 1451
  recently measured by Guber[1] as well as the recommended        5837 1451
  thermal constants. The fit was performed by the Bayesian R-     5837 1451
  matrix methodology implemented in the SAMMY code[2] starting    5837 1451
  from a revised set of ENDF/B-VIII.0 resonance parameter[3].     5837 1451
  Due to the lack of experimental details, other available        5837 1451
  measured data were not included in the R-matrix fit. A more     5837 1451
  detailed description of the reasoning behind this can be found  5837 1451
  in [4]. Only their overall agreement with the evaluted          5837 1451
  parameters was checked. Additionally, the mass was updated to   5837 1451
  be in agreement with [5].                                       5837 1451
                                                                  5837 1451
  To describe the contribution of the external resonance levels,  5837 1451
  two energy levels above 200 keV and two levels below zero were  5837 1451
  defined. Additionally, a third negative resonance level was     5837 1451
  added to better fit the thermal values.                         5837 1451
                                                                  5837 1451
  Based of the chi-squared metric, several energy levels were     5837 1451
  changed from s-wave to p-wave to better agree with the measured 5837 1451
  data. Additional p-waves were added where they could be seen in 5837 1451
  the new measurements. No unresolved resonance parameters were   5837 1451
  evaluated.                                                      5837 1451
                                                                  5837 1451
  Although Ce-140 capture cross section can include a direct      5837 1451
  capture contribution, this was accounted by sub-threshold       5837 1451
  levels.                                                         5837 1451
