    with experimental data obtained by Ohkubo[9] in the energy    5837 1451
    range from 2.5437 keV to 55.113 keV.  Parameters of the       5837 1451
    negative resonance were re-adjusted to the above thermal cross5837 1451
    sections [8].                                                 5837 1451
