    modified on the basis of Ohkubo et al. [10]. Capture widths   5837 1451
    of all levels were multiplied by a factor of 1.4 so as to be  5837 1451
    consistent with a new capture cross section measurement[11].  5837 1451
    A negative level was modified and 1/v corresction was aplied  5837 1451
    to the capture cross section.                                 5837 1451
